As part of the New Circular Economy Action Plan, the European Commission proposed the Ecodesign for Sustainable Products Regulation (ESPR) in March 2022. This regulation aims to address products’ most harmful environmental impacts and to transition society from a linear approach to a circular approach to conducting business.

Our governance and policies on environmental protection The Siemens’ Chief People and Sustainability Officer, a mem-

ber of the Managing Board, works to ensure that we operate in compliance with our environmental guidelines. Our EHS Principles serve as internal binding guidelines for this purpose.